    "Test" : {

    },
    "The Adhan reminder fires this many minutes before the jamaat time set below." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ينطلق تذكير الأذان قبل وقت الجماعة المحدد أدناه بهذا العدد من الدقائق."
          }
        },
        "bn" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "নিচে নির্ধারিত জামাতের সময়ের এত মিনিট আগে আজানের রিমাইন্ডার বাজবে।"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ezan hatırlatıcısı, aşağıda ayarlanan cemaat vaktinden bu kadar dakika önce çalar."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The closest a servant is to his Lord is while prostrating." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "أَقْرَبُ مَا يَكُونُ الْعَبْدُ مِنْ رَبِّهِ وَهُوَ سَاجِدٌ."
          }
        },
        "bn" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "বান্দা তার রবের সবচেয়ে নিকটবর্তী হয় সিজদারত অবস্থায়।"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kulun Rabbine en yakın olduğu an secde hâlidir."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The coolness of my eyes is in prayer." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "وَجُعِلَتْ قُرَّةُ عَيْنِي فِي الصَّلَاةِ."
          }
        },
        "bn" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "আমার চোখের শীতলতা রাখা হয়েছে নামাজে।"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Gözümün nuru namazda kılındı."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The first deed for which a servant will be held accountable on the Day of Judgment is the prayer." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "أَوَّلُ مَا يُحَاسَبُ بِهِ الْعَبْدُ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ الصَّلَاةُ."
          }
        },
        "bn" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "কিয়ামতের দিন বান্দার সর্বপ্রথম যে আমলের হিসাব নেওয়া হবে তা হলো নামাজ।"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kıyamet günü kulun hesaba çekileceği ilk amel namazdır."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The focus cover will dismiss automatically after the duration. If the dismiss button is disabled, the overlay is persistent to aid discipline." : {

    },
